I had something similar happen to me last night, I figured it might have been a fluke but seeing this makes me think it potentially might not be now.<br>
<br>
The situation: In Vex Thal killing TVK. After watching wizard after wizard being killed due to crits (I only have SCF so I don't crit all that often) I was nuking very slow and measured with Concussion thrownin between. Anyway TVK gets down to about 30 health and we get repops which I help kill. I'm now close to OOM so I stop Nuking, use BOTH harvests, then click a modrod. I am IMMEDIATELY summoned and killed by TVK (hi quad 2k damage)<br>
<br>
I had stopped nuking TVK for a while since I stopped to deal with the add, and used BOTH harvests. That should have really moved me down the agro list. I had NOT nuked to re-engage TVK between the add, harvests and using the Modrod.<br>
<br>
Agro from the mod-rod was IMMEDIATE, almost like I clicked a <br>
&quot;hi kill me now please&quot; button. I think this wierdness is related now to these other goofy agro issues.<br>
